# Deployment Environment Variables

## Backend (Railway/Render/Heroku)
MONGODB_URI=mongodb+srv://username:password@cluster0.xxxxx.mongodb.net/digiboard?retryWrites=true&w=majority&appName=Cluster0
NODE_ENV=production
PORT=5000

## Frontend Build Configuration
FLUTTER_WEB_API_URL=https://your-backend-url.railway.app/api

## MongoDB Atlas Setup
# 1. Go to https://www.mongodb.com/cloud/atlas/register
# 2. Create free cluster (M0 Sandbox)
# 3. Create database user
# 4. Get connection string
# 5. Replace <password> and <dbname> in connection string
